  m_text: "    <size=40><b>The Wolf</b><size=30>\n<color=#F3C071>Beats fox.\nUpgraded:
    +1 Score for each adjacent allied wolf<color=#B4B4B4>\n\n     <size=40><b>The
    Fox</b><size=30>\n<color=#F3C071>Beats rabbit. \nUpgraded: Scores against diagonals,
    negates upgraded rabbits<color=#B4B4B4>\n\n     <size=40><b>The Rabbit</b><size=30>\n<color=#F3C071>Beats
    wolf. \nUpgraded: Immune to and beats foxes<color=#B4B4B4>\n\nBeasts are upgraded
    while scoring against an ally"
